<section class="hero is-fullheight">
  <div class="hero-head">
     <nav class="navbar" data-controller="dropdown">
      <div class="is-flex">
        <div class="navbar-item">
          <span class="is-flex is-align-content-center">
            <span>
              <%= link_to root_path do %>
                <figure class="image mr-2" style="height: 1.9rem;">
                  <img src="/icon-dark.png" alt="Fliprr Logo" style="max-height: 100% !important; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: center; ">
                </figure>
              <% end %>
            </span>
            <span class="is-size-5-fullhd is-size-6-widescreen is-size-7-desktop is-hidden-touch is-align-content-center"> is the latest <strong class="has-text-black has-text-weight-extrabold">secondhand device e-commerce management platform</strong> partnered with
              <strong class="has-text-black has-text-weight-extrabold"><%= link_to "Not All Ones and Zeros", "https://www.notallonesandzeros.com", class: "has-text-success" %></strong>
            </span>
          </span>
        </div>

        <span class="navbar-burger dropdown is-right" data-dropdown-target="dropdown" data-action="click->dropdown#toggle" data-target="navbarMenuHeroA" aria-label="Menu">
          <div class="dropdown-trigger">
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
          </div>

          <div class="dropdown-menu" id="dropdown-menu" role="menu">
            <div class="dropdown-content">
              <% if current_user %>
                <div class="dropdown-item"><%= link_to "Dashboard", account_tables_path(current_user.accounts.first), class: "button is-dark is-fullwidth" %></div>
              <% else %>
                <div class="dropdown-item"><%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_registration_path, class: "button is-dark is-fullwidth" %></div>
                <div class="dropdown-item"><%= link_to "Log in", new_user_session_path, class: "button is-link is-fullwidth" %></div>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </span>
      </div>

      <div id="navMenu" class="navbar-menu">
        <div class="navbar-end">
          <div class="navbar-item">
            <div class="buttons">
              <% if current_user %>
                <%= link_to "Dashboard", account_tables_path(current_user.accounts.first), class: "button is-dark" %>
              <% else %>
                <%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_registration_path, class: "button is-dark" %>
                <%= link_to "Log in", new_user_session_path, class: "button is-link" %>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

  </div>
  <div class="hero-body has-text-centered">
    <div class="container has-text-centered">
      <h2 class="title is-size-1 container mb-6">Can't quite find the right fit for <br>your second hand device business?</h2>
      <div class="columns is-size-3 mb-6">
        <div class="column has-text-left">
          <div class="mb-4">There are plenty of e-commerce platforms out there, but most are designed for big businesses.</div>
          <div class="mb-4"><strong class="has-text-weight-extrabold"> They’re bloated, slow, and expensive—made for nobody in particular.</strong></div>
           We’re building Phone Fliprr to change that. It’s <strong class="has-text-weight-extrabold">fast, simple, and affordable,</strong> designed specifically for the needs of secondhand device businesses.
        </div>
        <div class="column has-text-left">
          <div class="mb-4"><strong class="has-text-weight-extrabold">Phone Fliprr</strong> is <strong class="has-text-weight-extrabold">new</strong>. We don’t have a huge marketing budget or years of history, but we do have a passionate team dedicated to building the best platform for sellers like you.</div>
          <div class="mb-4"><strong class="has-text-weight-extrabold">We’re constantly improving and adding features, and with your early support, we can make it even more powerful for your specific needs.</strong></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>Phone Fliprr is currently in <strong class="has-text-weight-extrabold">beta</strong>, and we’re looking for early adopters to help us shape the platform.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
